snippet.title: The result of a 100 hours of gameplay | Octavio Camacho
snippet.description: This is part 1 in a series of 100 hours of gameplay in the Octavio Camacho video game. This is the freewill mode with a team of raiders (pirates) deep in the urban warfare center ranking up.
